REACTION   (33-AS-75(N,2N)33-AS-74,,SIG,,AV)
REL-REF    (A,14291005,R.Raut+,J,PR/C,83,044621,2011)
           (A,,D.Brown+,J,NDS,148,1,2018) ENDF/B-VIII.0 value.
ANALYSIS   The average measured cross section is 966+-71 mb
           based on TOADs #1 and #2. Due to issues with the
           recovery time for TOAD #3, the uncertainty is far
           higher than for the other two, and it was used to
           verify the results from the other TOADs but not
           included in the average.
